Hugo Weihe, international 
specialist head of Indian art at Christie's and Tina Zonars, 
international director of Chinese works of art at Christie's, 
discuss investing in Asian art. Weihe and Zonars talk with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and Courtney Donohoe on  Bloomberg Radio 's 
"Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 10:09
 